1).  Static method cannot call a non-static method directly, we have to create an object
 of the class to call non-static methods.
2).  U can call a non-static method from another non-static method directly without creating objects.
3).  From static main method u can directly call another static method.
4).  Non-static method can directly call a static method

Static ---------------  Static allowed
Non-static --------- Nonstatic, static (allowed)
Static ---------------- from static methods non-static methods can be called only by creating an object of the class
Non-static method can directly call a static method